<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-7694] Expected Compaction Interruption is logged as ERROR</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-7694</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As seen in the attached log, occasionally a major compaction will interrupt other running compactions. This is not an error and is expected behavior. However this is logged at ERROR. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;OSX and Ubuntu 14.04&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
